1. List all customers

Query :-
SELECT * FROM Customers;

OUTPUT : - 
+------------+-----------+----------+------------------------+-------------+
| CustomerID | FirstName | LastName | Email                  | DateOfBirth |
+------------+-----------+----------+------------------------+-------------+
|          1 | John      | Doe      | john.doe@example.com   | 1985-01-15  |
|          2 | Jane      | Smith    | jane.smith@example.com | 1990-06-20  |
+------------+-----------+----------+------------------------+-------------+

